OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fpatchy cloud and clear spells along
OL,7,Fwith light winds. There is a chance of
OL,8,Fa little patchy mist forming late
OL,9,Ftonight in rural areas.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FDry with patchy cloud and
OL,12,Fsunny spells, once any early mist has
OL,13,Fcleared. It will be a warm day for
OL,14,Fmuch of the region by the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FTurning
OL,17,Fcooler and windier over the weekend
OL,18,Fwith an increased chance of some rain
OL,19,For showers. Monday probably drier but
OL,20,Fshowery rain might arrive later.
OL,21,FTemperatures warm, but cooler Sunday
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
